{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">AN OPEN-WORLD ACTION-ADVENTURE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to the beautiful yet brutal continent of Pywel. <br>From the snow-blasted mountains of Kweiden to the verdant expanses of Akapen and the towering ridges scattering the Crimson Desert, this land is a testament to nature's grandeur. Yet, amidst this beauty, the continent stands locked in war as factions vie for unprecedented power. <br> <br>Discover adventure, explore exciting locations, and fight thrilling battles as you travel across an incredible open world filled with wonder and mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/1.gif?t=1737363469\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KLIFF AND THE GREYMANES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;This is our mission.&quot;<br>Join Kliff, captain of the Greymanes, and his comrades as they embark on a relentless journey to defend Pywel and fulfill their mission.<br>Along your perilous path stands both dependable allies and countless foes who will stop at nothing to see your downfall.<br>Face trials to uncover the truth of the catastrophe looming over Pywel and restore peace to the continent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/2.gif?t=1737363469\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737363469","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737363469","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/83dc32a564f0e26e5cf80e20f88a6add63ada5fd/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737363469","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/83dc32a564f0e26e5cf80e20f88a6add63ada5fd/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=